%e A278299   +---+---+---+---+---+---+---+---+
%e A278299   | 6 | 9 | 8 | 3 | 6 | 7 | 8 | 1 |
%e A278299   +---+---+---+---+---+---+---+---+
%e A278299   | 10| 3 | 4 | 7 | 1 | 10| 5 |
%e A278299   +---+---+---+---+---+---+---+
%e A278299 From _Ryan Lee_, May 14 2019: (Start)
